room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Escape" by Escape the Room Dallas in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: It’s your chance to save the planet! Jurassic predators are being cloned and it’s up to you and nine friends to stop the dinosaurs from being released and wreaking havoc on the streets of Fort Worth. Protect the Stockyards, by avoiding detection from the evil corporation creating these experiments and stop their cloning process, all while eluding some loose dinosaurs in Jurassic Escape.
